- [ ] No circular imports
- [ ] Error handling for all async operations
- [ ] All promises are awaited
- [ ] Try/catch blocks for error handling
- [ ] No console.log in production code
- [ ] Functions are < 50 lines
- [ ] Cyclomatic complexity < 10
- [ ] Component props are properly typed
- [ ] React hooks dependencies correct
- [ ] No unnecessary re-renders
- [ ] Async functions have clear cancellation
- [ ] Environment variables validated at startup
- [ ] API calls handle timeouts
- [ ] Error messages are user-friendly
- [ ] Tests have descriptive names
- [ ] Coverage targets met (90%+ line)
- [ ] Mutation tests pass (85%+ score)
- [ ] Linter (ESLint) passes without warnings
- [ ] Type checker passes in strict mode
- [ ] No deprecated dependencies
```

{% else -%}
```
Code Quality Checklist - {{ language | capitalize }}:
- [ ] All functions have documentation
- [ ] Consistent naming conventions followed
- [ ] No unused variables or imports
- [ ] Error handling implemented
- [ ] Edge cases handled
